Bug is in code that extracts resource from selection, which doesn't tolerate
IAdaptables that don't adapt to IResource:

IResource resource = (IResource)adaptable.getAdapter(IResource.class);
projects.add(resource.getProject());

Should be:

IResource resource = (IResource)adaptable.getAdapter(IResource.class);
if (resource != null)
   projects.add(resource.getProject());
